{"tid":699773,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[[食鬼亂煮系列]]---Country Style Mushroom Boule","createTime":"2018-06-12T19:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T06:26:45.000Z","uid":182683,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"448802394bf32ca9e688c39aa616f71bbb7ab3f1","tid":699773,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T19:59:44.000Z","msg":"上次整完傻,今次教番整包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />. 西式勁硬個啲包大家都應該食過,但我我見出面好少有用蘑菇黎整包,就比大家試試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n依個食譜係一個係farmer's market賣包既人教我,就算係外國都比較少用蘑菇直接加落個包到,食落幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/13/xiD2hH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2FxiD2hH.jpg&h=2aaac9db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次我會用到autolyse依個技巧,會令到麵團自己產生麵筋,去到mixing嘅時候就可以減少時間,更加保持到小麥嘅香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,通常你會見到應用係sourdough到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .<br />\n想知多啲麵筋方面嘅野可以ig dm 問番我,盡量答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n<br />\n份量:1-2人<br />\n<br />\n材料:<br />\n高筋麵粉 140g<br />\n全麥麵粉 44g<br />\nwheat bran 8g(如果搵唔到可以用麥片代替/唔落)<br />\n水 121g<br />\n<br />\n乾酵母 2g<br />\n鹽 5g<br />\n<br />\nPortobello mushroom 100g<br />\n油<br />\n黑胡椒<br />\n<br />\n做法:<br />\n前一日(step 1,2,3):<br />\n1.高筋麵粉,全麥麵粉,wheat bran,水搵手攪到變成一舊唔光滑嘅麵團,見唔到麵粉就可以,冚好放係室溫2個鐘.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/13/6HlYLW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F6HlYLW.jpg&h=818ba26a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.放左2個鐘你會見到已經拉到薄膜,跟住基本上唔駛狂搓都夠麵筋去支撐個包.<br />\n落乾酵母同鹽,不段將外圍麵團摺入中間,直到乾酵母同鹽撈混為止.<br />\n之後將麵團向住個盆壓落去搓5分鐘到就可以冚好發酵半個鐘.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/13/yoLmrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2FyoLmrV.jpg&h=ba0262c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.過左半個鐘做一次folding,拍走麵團啲氣,將四面摺入中間.<br />\n過半個鐘做多一次,你會見到麵團光滑左好多,包好保鮮紙,放入雪櫃最少雪8個鐘(我通常雪過夜冇理幾耐).<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/13/IKe4tb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2FIKe4tb.jpg&h=6c0157bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第日:<br />\n1.拎麵團出黎等佢變番室溫,大概30-60分鐘.<br />\n等緊既時間可以煮蘑菇,蘑菇切厚啲(5mm-7mm),落油,黑胡椒炒到軟身熟曬,放上吸油紙備用.<br />\n記得一定要索番多餘既油,如果唔係會好難加入麵團.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/13/xe28tv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2Fxe28tv.jpg&h=f4a67c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.用手壓平舊麵,鋪曬啲菇上去,上下對摺,落少少麵粉,麵團中間切一半將兩舊重疊再用手壓一壓,不斷重複中間開半將兩舊重疊再用手壓一壓,直到啲菇混沌為止.<br />\n開頭麵團會好濕因為啲菇會出水,真係太濕就落少少麵粉,你不斷重複上面講個個動作佢慢慢就會變番到正常麵團質地.<br />\nPre-shape做半圓,冚好個面等20分鐘.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/13/o3LcKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2Fo3LcKH.jpg&h=62fb6961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.落少少麵粉,反轉麵團,拍走啲氣,將外邊嘅麵團不斷摺入中間整到半圓形,直到感覺到有阻力為止.<br />\n掃走木板上嘅麵粉,麵團底向下,用兩隻手包住麵團向自己方向拉後,麵團轉幾次方向重複幾次,利用木板嘅摩擦力收緊底部,見到個表面光滑,底部痴實就可以停.<br />\n平均撒麵粉落個banneton到(冇用個圓盆墊塊布再撒麵粉),驚痴住嘅話撒多少少唔怕.<br />\n麵團面向下,底向上放落去,包好等45分鐘/2倍大(我整個時室溫係26&deg;C).<br />\n焗爐提早20分鐘開230&deg;C,放個入得焗爐嘅煲連蓋一齊預熱.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/13/7xbPLG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F7xbPLG.jpg&h=9aec7c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.發酵完成,拎個煲出黎,反轉個麵團輕輕放上牛油紙上面,用刀隨意𠝹一刀,連牛油紙放入煲到,用水壺噴少少水入去,冚蓋.<br />\n230&deg;C焗15分鐘,開蓋,轉210&deg;C焗25-30分鐘.<br />\n出左爐記得等到凍曬先好切黎食,如果唔係個包會變形.<br />\n𠝹包個到其實大有學問係到,如果大家想知多啲可以ig dm問我,我有相關既資料同經驗.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/13/TlPp5X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2FTlPp5X.jpg&h=e00bbb1b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/13/Lk3VpZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2FLk3VpZ.jpg&h=27c2e5b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/13/cKwV9E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2FcKwV9E.jpg&h=1ac65c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲人可能會話屋企整包好煩,但係一朝早起身聞到焗包個個味係正到形容唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n啖啖蘑菇加埋啲黑胡椒,仲有啲麥味,牛油都唔駛用已經超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一個人一日食曬成個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n因為有蘑菇嘅關系,個包最好3日內食曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n<br />\nig:hkfoodghost<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d770e76867878d538d1bb16ff752304b22127220","tid":699773,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25047909d53f4588e5d418e3b614a8f5d4922dd","tid":699773,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0bbc5c9344e356b1e58c530edb45731b23e6be","tid":699773,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:34:46.000Z","msg":"打得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4aa4dd1b3f2c97122f16b9d08f858be4e200d9","tid":699773,"uid":116390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"睇晒<br />\n支持下"},{"pid":"188dc14577482beb462aa7f6261114a0697122e5","tid":699773,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd4aa4dd1b3f2c97122f16b9d08f858be4e200d9","tid":699773,"uid":116390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"睇晒<br />\n支持下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你 有興趣整下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037d056185a9e06e7852644ab8a455da2a307b0a","tid":699773,"uid":120093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:56:23.000Z","msg":"我都想試下俾麵包香整醒， 但點預發酵時間？ 用雪櫃發拎返出黎都要等喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7375af0d390b14011c3550b0d600ce0e48fcdfb3","tid":699773,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:57:36.000Z","msg":"食鬼整畀我食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421c57dad379d1e4cc51513d8ec20e986bd9cd6c","tid":699773,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"037d056185a9e06e7852644ab8a455da2a307b0a","tid":699773,"uid":120093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:56:23.000Z","msg":"我都想試下俾麵包香整醒， 但點預發酵時間？ 用雪櫃發拎返出黎都要等喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫你女朋友早啲起身整比你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b286fc4d7d8e5fb81b149e18415286c1e179c5","tid":699773,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7375af0d390b14011c3550b0d600ce0e48fcdfb3","tid":699773,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:57:36.000Z","msg":"食鬼整畀我食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:41:02.000Z","msg":"教你都得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc95a147c3e4edce3a50052f2f571c7427256e29","tid":699773,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99b286fc4d7d8e5fb81b149e18415286c1e179c5","tid":699773,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7375af0d390b14011c3550b0d600ce0e48fcdfb3","tid":699773,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:57:36.000Z","msg":"食鬼整畀我食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:41:02.000Z","msg":"教你都得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:59:32.000Z","msg":"懶鬼求包養<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dab2d341e4e5d8532ffe2fd23b589522261fd0c","tid":699773,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc95a147c3e4edce3a50052f2f571c7427256e29","tid":699773,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99b286fc4d7d8e5fb81b149e18415286c1e179c5","tid":699773,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7375af0d390b14011c3550b0d600ce0e48fcdfb3","tid":699773,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:57:36.000Z","msg":"食鬼整畀我食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:41:02.000Z","msg":"教你都得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:59:32.000Z","msg":"懶鬼求包養<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d21a12d933fd57759b58f163b3d93157a4b355","tid":699773,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dab2d341e4e5d8532ffe2fd23b589522261fd0c","tid":699773,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc95a147c3e4edce3a50052f2f571c7427256e29","tid":699773,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"